| Priority | Smell | Fix | Why First |
|----------|-------|-----|-----------|
| 1 | Assertion-Free Test | Add assertions | Prevents false-pass — highest risk |
| 2 | Conditional Logic | Split into two tests | Hidden untested path |
| 3 | Sleepy Test | Await instead of sleep | Flakiness + slow suite |
| 4 | Mystery Guest | Inline test data | Broken on CI / other machines |
| 5 | Exception Handling | Use `Assert.ThrowsException` | Quick one-line swap |
| 6 | Sensitive Equality | Assert on properties | Quick swap, removes fragility |
